high_descs: Turn right and walk to face the kitchen counter just right of the sink
Pick up the fork from the counter
Turn in a circle and face the same counter
Open the top drawer and put the fork in it
anns.task_desc: Put the fork in the kitchen drawer

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fork on the counter.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Move back away slightly from the top drawer in front of you.
Open the top drawer in front of you and put the fork in it.
anns.task_desc: Move a fork from a counter top to a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to the counter on the right.
Pick up the fork next to the potato.
Turn around in a full circle.
Open the drawer and put the fork inside.
anns.task_desc: Put the fork from the counter into the drawer.
